Afrika bɛ jiɲɛ jɔyɔrɔ flanan na boya ani caya la kun cɛla, Asia kɔ. A boya bɛse 30.2 million km² (11.7 million sq mi)krefɛ gunw fralen a kan, a  ye 6% Dugukolo fɛnsɛn bakrunba la. Afrika dugudunw ye mɔgɔ 922 million (kata 2005). A bɛ talikɛ Jiɲɛ hamaden 14.2%. Gun in lamununen ni Mediterane Kɔgɔji Saheli fɛ, Suez Bajalan ani Kɔgɔji Blen SaheliKɔrɔn fɛ, Indika Kɔgɔji Worodugukɔrɔn fɛ, ani Atlantik Kɔgɔji tlebi fɛ. A lakafolen jamana 46 kafara Madagaskar kan.
